This paper deals with online convex optimization, which is a subfield of machine learning and optimization. The paper specifically focuses on stochastic sub-gradient observation faults, which is a problem that arises in many machine learning applications. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also deals with optimization of learning rates, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY).
